      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand mb-3">Get an Industry-Specific SEO Audit</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">I will analyse your industry's search landscape in Guildford, identify the keywords your competitors are ranking for, and show you exactly where the opportunities are.</p>
